<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>DevOps Portal</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background: #f4f6f9;
      color: #333;
      text-align: center;
    }
    header {
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #007BFF, #00C851);
      color: white;
      padding: 30px 20px;
    }
    header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 2.5em;
    }
    header p {
      margin-top: 10px;
      font-size: 1.2em;
    }
    section {
      padding: 40px 20px;
    }
    .cards {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 20px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .card {
      background: white;
      padding: 20px;
      width: 250px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      transition: transform 0.2s ease;
    }
    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
    }
    .card h3 {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: #007BFF;
    }
    footer {
      background: #222;
      color: #bbb;
      padding: 20px;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>🚀 DevOps Portal</h1>
    <p>Continuous Integration | Continuous Delivery | Automation</p>
  </header>

  <section>
    <h2>Key Pillars of DevOps</h2>
    <div class="cards">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>CI/CD</h3>
        <p>Automated pipelines for building, testing, and deploying applications faster.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Infrastructure as Code</h3>
        <p>Manage and provision infrastructure using tools like Terraform and Ansible.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Monitoring</h3>
        <p>Ensure reliability and performance with tools like Prometheus, Grafana, and ELK.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Collaboration</h3>
        <p>Bringing developers and operations teams together to deliver value continuously.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <p>© 2025 DevOps Portal | Built for Learning & Innovation</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
